========================== SetCCOPTS v1.00 ===========================
======================================================================
There is not much to say about this small utilitie.  I think everybody
who's dealing with Aztec C 5.0 knows why this had to be done.

=========================== Installation =============================
======================================================================
SetCCOPTS requires the req.library. Put the library into LIBS:.

============================== Usage =================================
======================================================================
SetCCOPTS is only controlled via gadgets:

   You can select an option by clicking on it's corresponding gadget.
   Then the gadget will become highlighted.

   Previous Page | Next Page     choose between the two (PAL) or three 
                                 (NTSC) pages of options.

   ABOUT ......	  Gives information about author
   QUIT .......	  Exit SetCCOPTS
   LOAD .......	  Load previously saved setting of CCOPTS
   SAVE(AS)....	  Save setting of CCOPTS to file
   SET ........	  Sets the CCOPTS environment variable
   GET ........	  Gets the CCOPTS environment variable from memory
   DEFAULTS ...	  Sets CCOPTS to default compiler setting
   REMOVE .....	  Removes the CCOPTS environment variable from memory

